<br>
He's up every patch day without fail.  If he's gonna pop, it'll be on patch day.  If you camp all day patch day and don't see him up, then chances are somebody got to him when you weren't looking.  Wait 5 days.  If patch was Thursday, then 1 Fri 2 Sat 3 Sun 4 Mon 5 Tues.  He'll pop some day on Tuesday.  Of course, chances are the next Wed or Thurs will be a patch day so you'll have another shot at him in a day or two if you miss out on his respawn. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=14092"><img src="http://users.easystreet.com/korb/images/eq/korby59-pon-nk-sig.jpg" border="0"></a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=turomtoesmasher>Turom Toesmasher</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 457<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/18/02 7:57 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.gaiahealing.com/everquest/turom_head.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Sev</span><hr size=1> Sev pops every 3 days, plus 0-24 hours.  This means that on a server/zone reset, he can spawn anywhere from instantly to 24 hours afterwards. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tugurok>Tugurok</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://mywebpages.comcast.net/bdiebold5/minitug.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 154<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/18/02 10:08 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span